{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Up and down, up-- and I don't know whether he wanted to help me or kill me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "But I was dangling in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And he put me down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And then the kommandant threw water down on us and made him stop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And I passed out kind of halfway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And he kept saying, whore, whore, with three men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "You know, night party, and things like that, over the loudspeaker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And the next morning, over the loudspeaker, to make sure that everybody could hear that he has found, and these were three student elders there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "In other words, who were in charge of that thing, and one woman, had a little orgy there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And to discourage others from doing so, he ordered [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "The Belgians could get packages-- we, from Holland, couldn't get anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "But they could get clean clothing and books or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "So-- and the cigarette ration-- which were, I think, Swiss cigarettes-- a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "Because-- and if they didn't like it, they could come to me and complain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't move at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I had muscles I didn't even know I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I literally could not move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet I went down the next morning-- don't me ask me how.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember what we did as children, my twin and I, when it was too boring for us to slide down the banister, we slid down on the-- on the steps, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how I got down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember this from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, I couldn't figure out why I had liked that when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't really all that funny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Down the steps, into the gym class-- you know, where they had gymnastic.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
